Package: NIRSVascMuscle
Title: NIRSVascMuscle: Package for NIRS Data Analysis in Muscle Physiology
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Dimitrios", "Megaritis", email = "megaritisdimitrios@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6786-4346"))
Description: This package provides tools for analyzing Near-Infrared Spectroscopy (NIRS) data in the context of muscle physiology research. It includes functions for data cleaning, event slicing, aggregation, heterogeneity, and on-off transient analysis across multiple channels.
License: Apache License 2.0
